            "started_at" : "20260120T205710Z",
            "stderr" : "",
            "stdout" : "[openstudio.measure.OSRunner] <Info> User-inputed airtightness design value 13.5 (m^3/h-m^2) at 75.0 Pa converts to 2.0085514 (m^3/h-m^2) at 4 Pa\n[openstudio.measure.OSRunner] <Info> 4-sided area = 1098.97 m^2, 5-sided area = 1363.97 m^2, 6-sided area = 1628.97 m^2.\n[openstudio.measure.OSRunner] <Info> 5-sided infiltration design value 0.0005579 (m^3/s-m^2) converted to 0.0005579 (m^3/s-m^2) based on 5-sided area 1363.97 m^2 and 5-sided area 1363.97 m^2 excluding ground boundary surfaces for energyplus.\n[openstudio.measure.OSRunner] <Warn> The largest airloop or HVAC system serves 0.0 m^2, which is less than 5% of the building area 1325.0 m^2. Attempting to use building hours of operation schedule instead.\n[openstudio.measure.OSRunner] <Warn> Unable to determine building hours of operation schedule. Treating the building as if there is no HVAC system schedule.\n[openstudio.measure.OSRunner] <Warn> Unable to determine the HVAC schedule. Treating the building as if there is no HVAC system with outdoor air.  If this is not the case, input a schedule argument, or assign one to an air loop in the model.\n[openstudio.measure.OSRunner] <Info> Using climate zone 6A from user arguments.\n[openstudio.measure.OSRunner] <Info> Using building type HighriseApartment from user arguments.\n[openstudio.measure.OSRunner] <Info> The modeled started with 0 infiltration objects and 0 effective leakage area objects.\n[openstudio.measure.OSRunner] <Info> The modeled finished with 50 infiltration objects.\n",
